  "name": "Deadweight Mutagen (Major)",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> Interact</p>\n<p>For 1 hour your joints loosen and bones thicken, making your body incredibly weighty and difficult to maneuver around.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit</strong> You gain a +4 item bonus to Athletics checks to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.7blmbDrQFNfdT731]{Shove} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.ge56Lu1xXVFYUnLP]{Trip}, to your Fortitude and Reflex DCs against attempts to Shove or Trip you, and to saving throws against effects that attempt to force you to move or knock you @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.j91X7x0XSomq8d60]{Prone}. You can attempt to Shove or Trip creatures up to three sizes larger than you.</p>\n<p><strong>Drawback</strong> You gain the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.D5mg6Tc7Jzrj6ro7]{Encumbered} condition and can't remove it while under the effects of the mutagen.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-effects.Item.7eCUXYunzGVEsaKh]{Effect: Deadweight Mutagen (Major)}</p>"
